        >
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border px-2.5 py-0.5 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 text-foreground border-border bg-background/70 font-mono text-[11px] font-normal backdrop-blur-[6px] transition-colors hover:bg-background"
          >
            <span
              class="hero-rainbow"
            >
              v2.10.0 · canvas design system
            </span>
          </div>
        </a>
        <h1
